# ==============================================
# Deployment Instructions
# ==============================================
# 
# To set these on Heroku:
# 
# Option 1: Using Heroku CLI
# heroku config:set IMGFLIP_USERNAME=your_value -a your-app-name
# heroku config:set IMGFLIP_PASSWORD=your_value -a your-app-name
# ... (repeat for all variables)
#
# Option 2: Bulk set from this file (after removing comments)
# cat .env | xargs heroku config:set -a your-app-name
#
# Option 3: Using Heroku Dashboard
# Go to: https://dashboard.heroku.com/apps/your-app-name/settings
# Click "Reveal Config Vars"
# Add each variable manually
#
# ==============================================
# Verification
# ==============================================
#
# To verify all variables are set:
# heroku config -a your-app-name
#
# To test a specific variable:
# heroku config:get IMGFLIP_USERNAME -a your-app-name
#
